{"tid":1452060,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"致仲想每日可以安穩返工的你 今日一點入機場","createTime":"2019-08-11T23:38:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T00:03:31.000Z","uid":72777,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ca26a28ffa1670263a914361fa7351389b0172c5","tid":1452060,"uid":72777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T23:38:52.000Z","msg":"各位 香港已經唔正常 唔會再有如常返工既安穩日子<br />\n如果大家再做鴕鳥 保證你日後就算日日返足24個鐘頭工都只可以食樹皮<br />\n因為香港會正式淪為一個大陸城巿 外資會走路 法治會崩潰 我地每一日都會活係恐懼不安之中<br />\n今日真係不宜返工<br />\n港豬如我都會請半日假 一點直入機場<br />\n跪求大家 今日罷工 企出黎 就係為左保住自己份工 請支持機場集會行動<br />\n記住不入禁區 不衝跑道 保護自己 守衛香港<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/E4d23UG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FE4d23UG.jpg&h=946ff9a1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cb0c1e3e1579d5080538b128c36c9c842e3f3bea","tid":1452060,"uid":125079,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T23:39:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9hXOZur.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9hXOZur.jpg&h=817ec132&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8ec876ff50b9e49bd230870d2bbce1edcc838aab","tid":1452060,"uid":125079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T23:39:37.000Z","msg":"全部 今日 1點 入機場"},{"pid":"c934295da9dffaba8e91212280104a780f73f350","tid":1452060,"uid":72777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T23:40:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99b91e59c99db6b5a8ea05b8f2746c5eb1e1a9ee","tid":1452060,"uid":260325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T23:41:11.000Z","msg":"波已射"},{"pid":"8b4acc962b6f1876cc1b7713680418edbac50e6d","tid":1452060,"uid":72777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T23:44:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b37695a7a88145b10acb134e900